social_posts.post_text: Pardon the self-tooting but it’s award nom season and I didn’t get a chance to share these earlier! Nice press and acknowledgment of the T&B team’s excellent work, from a few of my fave cultural critics! 💗😌✌️ Vote for Tooky and Beebo!

Listen to my pal Raphael: Donate any amount to abortion funds by December 12 and you might win an original sketch of your fave character from BoJack OR Tuca!! Instructions in slide 3 ! 🌱 Three winners will be chosen and I am prepared to draw three BoJacks if that’s what you all want!!
Bored of AI “art” 😴

Oh my goodness, thank you to everyone who donated and entered this raffle, you raised $10,120.40 for abortion funds! And the winners chose three great characters, fun for me to revisit: Draca (new shoes, tits out), Princess Carolyn (sassy as ever), and a current day Diane (still writing and living her best life). Thank you all! 💗

We got to visit @ranchlands recently and it was horsegirl heaven. 4+ hour rides every day at ~8k altitude. I got to ride Peach, an impatient palomino mare who would rather jig backwards than stand still, seemed to have IBS, and loved to race ahead of everyone in turbo-mode. Perfect horse, 10/10. The ranch staff and wranglers were so welcoming and the food was so good too?? This isn’t an ad, I just want to go back. Thank you, Zapata Ranch!
